Disk World creator help
query_mail_information

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_mail_information -  This method is used to print extra data in the mail message which gets sent.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string query_mail_information(string area,
class nomic_case the_case,
string type,
mixed data)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^area%^RESET%^ - the area the case is in
%^BOLD%^the_case%^RESET%^ - the case to work on
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of the punishment
%^BOLD%^data%^RESET%^ - the data associated with the punishment

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/punishment_inherit.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is used to print extra data in the mail message which
gets sent.  This should tell the person how to go about dealing with
whatever has happened to them.
.EP

